analysisPopulations.name: Enrolled subjects dataset
analysisPopulations.text: The enrolled subjects dataset will consist of all subjects who signed the informed consent form.
analysisPopulations.label: Enrolled
analysisPopulations.populationDescription: The enrolled subjects dataset will consist of all subjects who signed the informed consent form.

analysisPopulations.name: Lead-in subjects dataset
analysisPopulations.text: The lead-in subjects dataset will consist of all subjects who entered the lead-in period.
analysisPopulations.label: Lead-in
analysisPopulations.populationDescription: The lead-in subjects dataset will consist of all subjects who entered the lead-in period.

analysisPopulations.name: Full analysis dataset
analysisPopulations.text: The full analysis dataset will consist of all randomized subjects who received at least one dose of double-blind study medication during the short-term double-blind treatment period.
analysisPopulations.label: FAS
analysisPopulations.populationDescription: The full analysis dataset will consist of all randomized subjects who received at least one dose of double-blind study medication during the short-term double-blind treatment period.
analysisPopulations.criteria: Randomized AND received >=1 dose of double-blind study medication

analysisPopulations.name: Evaluable subjects dataset
analysisPopulations.text: The evaluable subjects dataset will consist of all subjects in the full analysis dataset who did not have any relevant protocol deviations.
analysisPopulations.label: Evaluable
analysisPopulations.populationDescription: The evaluable subjects dataset will consist of all subjects in the full analysis dataset who did not have any relevant protocol deviations.
analysisPopulations.criteria: Included in FAS AND no relevant protocol deviations

analysisPopulations.name: Treated subjects dataset
analysisPopulations.text: The treated subjects dataset will consist of all subjects who received at least one dose of double-blind study medication during the short-term double-blind treatment period.
analysisPopulations.label: Treated
analysisPopulations.populationDescription: The treated subjects dataset will consist of all subjects who received at least one dose of double-blind study medication during the short-term double-blind treatment period.
analysisPopulations.criteria: Received >=1 dose of double-blind study medication
